- This is a Multilingual app that invokes the Fifth Amendment rightMobile App (React Native):
- /components (UI components)
- /screens (app screens)
- /utils (utility functions)
- /api (API integrations)
- App.js (main app file
Desktop App (Xamarin/.NET):
- /Views (UI views)
- /ViewModels (view models)
- /Models (data models)
- /Services (business logic)
- App.xaml (main app file)

